---
// src/pages/project.astro
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

// You can add any page-specific frontmatter here.
// For instance, set a title or publish date.
const title = "My Amazing Project";
const publishDate = "March 10, 2025";
---
<Layout title={`${title} - Project`}>
  <main class="container mx-auto px-4 py-16">
    <article class="glass p-12 rounded-3xl max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <!-- Blog Post Header -->
      <header class="mb-8">
        <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold mb-2">{title}</h1>
        <p class="text-gray-200 text-lg">Published on {publishDate}</p>
      </header>

      <!-- Blog Post Content -->
      <section class="prose max-w-none text-gray-200">
        <p>
          Welcome to this detailed overview of my project. In this post, I'll discuss the background, the challenges I faced,
          and the cutting edge technologies I employed. Follow along as I walk you through the project.
        </p>

        <!-- Image Section -->
        <figure class="my-8">
          <img src="/project-screenshot.jpg" alt="Project Screenshot" class="rounded-2xl w-full" />
          <figcaption class="text-center text-sm text-gray-400 mt-2">
            A screenshot highlighting the main interface of the project.
          </figcaption>
        </figure>

        <!-- Project Details -->
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-10">Project Details</h2>
        <p>
          Here, you can delve into technical details, methodologies used, and insights into the development process. The design
          strategy behind the project is also explained in depth.
        </p>

        <!-- Embedded YouTube Video -->
        <div class="video-container my-8">
          <iframe 
            width="560" 
            height="315" 
            src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/La2TCeWXSwQ" 
            title="YouTube video player" 
            frameborder="0" 
            allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" 
            allowfullscreen 
            class="rounded-2xl w-full">
          </iframe>
        </div>

        <!-- Additional Content -->
        <p>
          I hope this post provides some insight into the complexities and creative processes behind my project. Stay tuned for more updates and follow my journey as I further develop new and exciting projects.
        </p>
      </section>
    </article>
  </main>
</Layout>
